data-triple-N3.o: "Index Fungorum is an international project to index all formal names in the Fungi Kingdom. It is somewhat comparable to the International Plant Names Index (IPNI), but with more contributing institutions. Another difference is that where IPNI does not indicate correct names, the Index Fungorum does indicate the status of a name. In the returns from the search page a currently correct name is indicated in green, while others are in blue (a few, aberrant usages of names are indicated in red)."@en
